/*
 * PRE-FLIGHT CHECKLIST
 * Mission         : Web patient/provider operation (bookings/profile/notes/dashboard)
 * DB Tables Used  : clients, providers, bookings, services
 * Concurrency Risk: NO — user-scoped operations
 * GCal Calls      : NO
 * Idempotency Key : NO — user-scoped reads
